{"tid":1277000,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[拋磚]國慶點攪","createTime":"2019-07-02T05:42:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T06:16:05.000Z","uid":52927,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"782277e0ba6270d5cb07a60cdaf3c4f9cc07fd56","tid":1277000,"uid":52927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:42:18.000Z","msg":"先唔好屌點解咁快諗咁遠先<br />\n<br />\n事源係見到CCTVB引用央視<br />\n話香港有暴徒動亂<br />\n既然央視都咁講 <br />\n我地梗係「附和」啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n整返個不消費運動<br />\n叫大陸人十一黃金週唔好黎香港<br />\n<br />\n唔安全呀 香港好得人驚呀<br />\n<br />\n香港人就 安坐家中 唔落街 唔消費<br />\n<br />\n定係跟返傳統 繼續遊行 集會 完"},{"pid":"8b860ca6c0d920ef93ce2ce33679a4725bbdf463","tid":1277000,"uid":204352,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:43:44.000Z","msg":"當天好多香港人都想去高鐵站迎接同胞到來<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23ba4221554ff8d477844c7e671c474b0b54bb9d","tid":1277000,"uid":52927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:44:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大陸人十一唔好黎"},{"pid":"d3aac5cb029b79193d8df37ce5da0c458e395c23","tid":1277000,"uid":127929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:46:49.000Z","msg":"默哀囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f3eb09b565f594693d3faa94157c9aa64307fba","tid":1277000,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:48:36.000Z","msg":"宜家直頭好似係唔放人黎旅遊"},{"pid":"08163c3278a4717193771f583688ef7b70e92a3a","tid":1277000,"uid":54927,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"23ba4221554ff8d477844c7e671c474b0b54bb9d","tid":1277000,"uid":52927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:44:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png